{"tid":419064,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港有咁多有錢人，但點解，冇人會選擇冷凍自己，等死後復活","createTime":"2017-09-30T06:44:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T01:56:31.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e13966e6a4618473520d3e3d08fe48291493c52c","tid":419064,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T06:44:27.000Z","msg":"人體冷凍技術（或人體冷藏學或人體冰凍法；英語：cryonics）是一種試驗中的醫學技術，把人體或動物在極低溫（一般在攝氏零下196度以下 / 華氏零下320以下）的情況下深低溫保存，並希望可以在未來通過先進的醫療科技使他們解凍後復活及治療。 <br />\n<br />\n人體冷凍技術被美國的《生活科學》雜誌（Live Science）列為十大人腦未解之謎之一，及十大超越人類極限的未來科學技術。 <br />\n<br />\n目前，最大型的人體冷藏公司為美國的阿爾科生命延續基金（Alcor Life Extension Foundation）和人體冷凍機構（Cryonics Institute）。 <br />\n<br />\n費用方面，人體冷凍機構的全身冷藏係28000美元，另加會員費，非會員收費係35000美元。人體冷凍機構會員費是120美元一年，或1250美元成為終身會員。阿爾科生命延續基金的全身冷藏，費用是200,000美元。 <br />\n<br />\n此外，人體冷藏者也可以考慮使用以人壽保險的形式付款，或分期付款繳交。 <br />\n<br />\n當計埋手術費同運費同行政費，由香港運去美國，要100萬港元。連埋冷凍費，用最貴的阿爾科生命延續基金，20萬美元，大約160港元。再俾多些空間。埋單都係300萬左右。再用多100萬reserve for 你復活，都唔會超400萬。平過香港好多300呎樓的價錢。 <br />\n<br />\n咁香港有咁多人連5000萬樓都買得起，倒底有幾多香港人會 join 呢個plan ?<br />\n<br />\n美國的阿爾科生命延續基金，是全球第一人體冷凍供應商，成立於1972年，樂意接受全球的人加入和成為冷凍者。截止2016年10月，香港區有 1 個會員。 <br />\n<br />\n人體冷凍機構，是全球第二大人體冷凍供應商，成立於1976年，樂意服務全球的人加入和成為冷凍者。截止2017年7月，香港區都係得1個會員。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTotal : 全港只有 2 個人，加入了人體冷凍的組織，成為會員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cryonics.org/ci-landing/member-statistics/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cryonics.org%2Fci-landing%2Fmember-statistics%2F&d=9gzO7v1m18dUcokXBQhKaDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=826850d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cryonics.org/ci-landing/member-statistics/</a> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.alcor.org/CryonicsMagazine/archive.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.alcor.org%2FCryonicsMagazine%2Farchive.html&d=9gzO7v1m18dUcokXBQhKaDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=36b8b8e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.alcor.org/CryonicsMagazine/archive.html</a>"},{"pid":"8499fa00a89803d41a14c14ce8f9cf24a6c5bfc6","tid":419064,"uid":28074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T06:51:06.000Z","msg":"因為份身家未洗晒"},{"pid":"cfdff1d1d8cfd1271be6a7411914a24277d66dee","tid":419064,"uid":70917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T06:55:16.000Z","msg":"香港樓價物價指數升得咁快，100年後誠哥<br />\n<br />\n都變窮人啦，復活後再次受苦<br />\n<br />\n冷凍不了"},{"pid":"e912b90f878f86fc799e39b5179b813a2370e6f2","tid":419064,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T06:59:39.000Z","msg":"冷凍嗰刻會唔會已經死咗㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d1091e2e43de05144fe9bb3931ee323baf156e","tid":419064,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:01:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冷凍嗰刻會唔會已經死咗㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有機會是會<br />\n冷凍就係要等將來科技發達可以將人體復活"},{"pid":"d6d88c5172e66d14131ea866ce92f0f58e73430f","tid":419064,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:03:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港樓價物價指數升得咁快，100年後誠哥<br />\n<br />\n都變窮人啦，復活後再次受苦<br />\n<br />\n冷凍不了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但科技類產品，如電腦，電視和智慧手機，就可以跌價之餘，兼比以前性能強大"},{"pid":"aed82037031ce0c9ad4e37e31e8b2c04783e6dc3","tid":419064,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:04:06.000Z","msg":"有錢人唔需要冷凍，窮人更加唔需要"},{"pid":"6349b0ece301801eaa8edbd5b37be24c61452b1a","tid":419064,"uid":62506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:07:03.000Z","msg":"因為樓主冇同佢地講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d751f582800c23b0ff10ed11948bfbe37dd56ed","tid":419064,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:11:10.000Z","msg":"安全風險？<br />\n法律問題？<br />\n生活適應問題？（假設成功）"},{"pid":"ebe7a8dae9e1b26d66e18c3a097149794c0689a8","tid":419064,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:17:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有錢人唔需要冷凍，窮人更加唔需要</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人生短暫，人最終要死<br />\n全世界最長壽都係122歲半<br />\n香港人死左多數火葬，火化<br />\n仲有少量會土葬，屍骨會十年後同泥土融合消失。<br />\n<br />\n就算講宗教，信神有永生和來世。香港雖然有好多人信宗教，但無神論都有不少。有不少人不信來生和永生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現家有科技復活的可能，人體冷凍呢個option 。<br />\n<br />\n我好好奇 ，點解咁多人有錢買幾千萬樓，都冇人選擇人體冷凍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反正點都要死，賭一賭博一博。"},{"pid":"032341c57d5ea45ac7d9d5c377e67aefde5a2654","tid":419064,"uid":49918,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:20:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ade7d2446d7d0a3c0c69b3a8d6b74274d1fb2b07","tid":419064,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:25:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有錢人同窮人既分別係，有錢用會把握所有看得見既機會，將利益最大化；而窮人就會將精神擺起不切實際既幻想中。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但今次觀察到的現象，剛同你相反，你話，利益最大化，反而班有錢人，冇人參加人體冷凍技術。全港只有2個會員，加入左人體冷凍相關組織，成為會員。"},{"pid":"32e9eb298310c519a8017a5741daeef86bbdf2da","tid":419064,"uid":49918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:38:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce3ed266dca9c6bfbfb64cc2d462a7316681adda","tid":419064,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:46:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有錢人同窮人既分別係，有錢用會把握所有看得見既機會，將利益最大化；而窮人就會將精神擺起不切實際既幻想中。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但今次觀察到的現象，剛同你相反，你話，利益最大化，反而班有錢人，冇人參加人體冷凍技術。全港只有2個會員，加入左人體冷凍相關組織，成為會員。</blockquote><br />\n因為個技術唔成熟，而且根本未有任何研究證明到人體可以復活，成件事根本同騙局無分別<br />\n<br />\n就正如一個富豪生cancer，你話自己識氣功可以有機會打散D cancer，收佢1000萬，你估佢會唔會睬你？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n還定都係死，博一博，好過被火化"},{"pid":"0bb306d615fbb6aa0bf2101e081f0798c22e546b","tid":419064,"uid":119379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:47:14.000Z","msg":"等，所有野都係得個等字<br />\n中間錯失左幾多野<br />\n醒番個陣個世界都唔同哂<br />\n所有野又要重新適應"},{"pid":"00eb082de935c86dc70ec4a61ea3c61492da45eb","tid":419064,"uid":50988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:48:17.000Z","msg":"通漲<br />\n<br />\n～完～"},{"pid":"65729176c408282d79ed32db1c0afb855dd00577","tid":419064,"uid":49918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:49:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"487ae1d154b61f3ef9bba7f68b5aec6db183747d","tid":419064,"uid":123296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:56:15.000Z","msg":"死咗唔放風水位 後人點繼續有錢？"},{"pid":"350ada862c1fbc19b401365e90f78d1fc17e13a9","tid":419064,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:57:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死咗唔放風水位 後人點繼續有錢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港唔係人人都信風水<br />\n好多信基督教，天主教，無神論，不可知論，自然神論等"},{"pid":"835b0d335265c137a31da33c3a1c42018ed65f6d","tid":419064,"uid":137132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:59:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>死咗唔放風水位 後人點繼續有錢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港唔係人人都信風水<br />\n好多信基督教，天主教，無神論，不可知論，自然神論等</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港大部分有錢人都信風水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90cb54d0efa4d4544a0567a22c6cb5f3edb89efb","tid":419064,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T08:04:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>死咗唔放風水位 後人點繼續有錢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港唔係人人都信風水<br />\n好多信基督教，天主教，無神論，不可知論，自然神論等</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港大部分有錢人都信風水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你確定? 咁郭氏三兄弟呢 ? <br />\n印象中有一批有錢人係基基，或天基。基督教有好多富人同中產。<br />\n應該仲有一批人信科學無神論，科學進化論。"},{"pid":"5c34ded7297ecba6879827978b93caca4f51d743","tid":419064,"uid":137132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T09:16:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>死咗唔放風水位 後人點繼續有錢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港唔係人人都信風水<br />\n好多信基督教，天主教，無神論，不可知論，自然神論等</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港大部分有錢人都信風水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你確定? 咁郭氏三兄弟呢 ? <br />\n印象中有一批有錢人係基基，或天基。基督教有好多富人同中產。<br />\n應該仲有一批人信科學無神論，科學進化論。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我確定全香港最有錢既誠哥係信風水"},{"pid":"c5cc1a14a97c3130386cfc2b703e81bc31a66c27","tid":419064,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T09:23:49.000Z","msg":"人體有大量水份<br />\n結冰膨脹導致細胞破裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88e35993a739459a88998945ca7ef5936775c33","tid":419064,"uid":31719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T09:49:31.000Z","msg":"你都唔係有錢人 點會明佢地呢"},{"pid":"a2c76d0ef075420630fce162fc911644065c300c","tid":419064,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T09:55:03.000Z","msg":"依家既技術話你聽凍完未死你都唔信啦"}]}